{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-template-jsx","path":"/blog/lae-totems/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>Territorios Sonoros Emergentes — <a href=\"https://audiostellar.xyz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AudioStellar</a></h1>\n<p>Territorios Sonoros Emergentes es una performance de danza y tecnología donde dos seres humanoides y una inteligencia artificial ensayan un rito en un bosque de pantallas de un amanecer distópico tratando de llegar a un equilibrio cósmico.</p>\n<br>\n<p><div class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\" style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden; \" > <div class=\"embedVideo-container\"> <iframe title=\"\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/SfAuaaqUlG4?rel=0\" class=\"embedVideo-iframe\" style=\"border:0; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; \" loading=\"lazy\" allowfullscreen=\"\" sandbox=\"allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-popups\"></iframe> </div> </div></p>\n<br>\n<p>Visuales: Santiago Fernandez y Ramiro Arsanto.<br>\nCuerpxs: Laila Meliz y Luca Gomez.<br>\nSonido: Leandro Garber, Dai Miauro.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>26/8/23 Laboratorio de Artes Electrónicas, Tecnópolis</p>","fields":{"slug":"/blog/lae-totems/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2023-8-26","title":"Territorios Sonoros Emergentes","image":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/ed231301b7b6b9d0e67dc3e836be38f3/3b049/portada_totems.jpg","srcSet":"/static/ed231301b7b6b9d0e67dc3e836be38f3/83e98/portada_totems.jpg 1020w,\n/static/ed231301b7b6b9d0e67dc3e836be38f3/6ee11/portada_totems.jpg 2040w,\n/static/ed231301b7b6b9d0e67dc3e836be38f3/3b049/portada_totems.jpg 4080w","sizes":"(min-width: 4080px) 4080px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/ed231301b7b6b9d0e67dc3e836be38f3/aca22/portada_totems.webp 1020w,\n/static/ed231301b7b6b9d0e67dc3e836be38f3/6f3ad/portada_totems.webp 2040w,\n/static/ed231301b7b6b9d0e67d